OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1772679804
OL,3,CHusband of Labour MP questioned after
OL,4,Carrest on suspicion of spying for China
OL,6,FThe husband of a Scottish Labour MP
OL,7,Fwas one of three men facing
OL,8,Fquestioning by police last night after
OL,9,Fbeing arrested on suspicion of spying
OL,10,Ffor China.
OL,12,FFollowing the arrest of her spouse
OL,13,FDavid Taylor, Joani Reid MP, who sits
OL,14,Fon the Home Affairs Select Committee,
OL,15,Fsaid she had "never seen anything to
OL,16,Fmake me suspect my husband has broken
OL,17,Fany law".
OL,26,@wD@NOUyD@HO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1772679804
OL,3,CHusband of Labour MP questioned after
OL,4,Carrest on suspicion of spying for China
OL,6,FThe arrests of the three men ` aged
OL,7,F39, 43 and 68 ` were carried out by
OL,8,Fcounter-terrorism officers at
OL,9,Faddresses in London and Wales on March
OL,10,F4 as they were accused of assisting a
OL,11,Fforeign intelligence service.
OL,13,FThe policing operation came as
OL,14,FSecurity Minister Dan Jarvis told MPs
OL,15,Fthat Chinese officials in the UK and
OL,16,FBeijing have been given a dressing
OL,17,Fdown, adding that the investigation
OL,18,Frelates to "foreign interference
OL,19,Ftargeting UK democracy".
OL,26,@zD@LOU{D@WO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1772679804
OL,3,CHusband of Labour MP questioned after
OL,4,Carrest on suspicion of spying for China
OL,6,FThe Metropolitan Police indicated late
OL,7,Fon Wednesday evening that all three
OL,8,Fremain in custody for questioning.
OL,10,FSearches have been carried out at the
OL,11,Faddresses where they were arrested.
OL,13,FThe force said that further updates
OL,14,Fcould be expected on Thursday morning.
OL,16,FMet officers were seen at a property
OL,17,Flinked to one of the men in South
OL,18,FWales.
OL,20,FA car outside the address has also
OL,21,Fbeen searched and photographed.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1772679804
OL,3,CHusband of Labour MP questioned after
OL,4,Carrest on suspicion of spying for China
OL,6,FFollowing the arrests, Ms Reid ` the
OL,7,FMP for East Kilbride and Strathaven `
OL,8,Fsaid in a statement: "I have never
OL,9,Fbeen to China. I have never spoken on
OL,10,FChina or China-related matters in the
OL,11,FCommons. I have never asked a question
OL,12,Fon China-related matters.
OL,14,F"As far as I am aware, I have never
OL,15,Fmet any Chinese businesses whilst I
OL,16,Fhave been an MP, any Chinese diplomats
OL,17,For government employees, nor raised
OL,18,Fany concern with ministers or anyone
OL,19,Felse on behalf of, even
OL,20,Fcoincidentally, Chinese interests.
OL,26,@pD@VOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1772679804
OL,3,CHusband of Labour MP questioned after
OL,4,Carrest on suspicion of spying for China
OL,6,F"I am a social democrat who believes
OL,7,Fin freedom of expression, free trade
OL,8,Funions and free elections.
OL,10,F"I am not any sort of admirer or
OL,11,Fapologist for the Chinese Communist
OL,12,FParty's dictatorship.
OL,14,F"I have never seen anything to make me
OL,15,Fsuspect my husband has broken any law.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1772679804
OL,3,CHusband of Labour MP questioned after
OL,4,Carrest on suspicion of spying for China
OL,6,F"I am not part of my husband's
OL,7,Fbusiness activities and neither I nor
OL,8,Fmy children are part of this
OL,9,Finvestigation, and we should not be
OL,10,Ftreated by media organisations as
OL,11,Fthough we are. Above all I expect
OL,12,Fmedia organisations to respect my
OL,13,Fchildren's privacy."
OL,15,FTaylor, 39, is listed as a "lobbyist"
OL,16,Fon Ms Reid's MP registered interests.
OL,18,FCompanies House names him as the
OL,19,Fdirector of Earthcott Limited, a
OL,20,Fpublic relations and communications
OL,21,Ffirm.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@TO]wD@\OUwD@eO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1772679804
OL,3,CHusband of Labour MP questioned after
OL,4,Carrest on suspicion of spying for China
OL,6,FEarlier, Home Office minister Mr
OL,7,FJarvis said there will be "severe
OL,8,Fconsequences" if it is proven that
OL,9,FChina attempted to interfere with UK
OL,10,Fsovereign affairs.
OL,12,FMr Jarvis said the investigation
OL,13,F"relates to China" and "foreign
OL,14,Finterference targeting UK democracy".
OL,16,FHe told MPs: "Let me be clear, if
OL,17,Fthere is proven evidence of attempts
OL,18,Fby China to interfere with UK
OL,19,Fsovereign affairs, we will impose
OL,20,Fsevere consequences and hold all
OL,21,Factors involved to account.
OL,26,@oD@[OUpD@MO]uD@AOUuD@RO]uD@XOUvD@dO]xD@
OL,26,ANOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30308
