CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1772679804
OL,3,CHusband of Labour MP questioned after
OL,4,Carrest on suspicion of spying for China
OL,6,F"The Government is taking robust
OL,7,Faction to ensure the UK's democratic
OL,8,Finstitutions and processes are a hard
OL,9,Ftarget for this activity.
OL,11,F"The National Security Act provides
OL,12,Four intelligence agencies and law
OL,13,Fenforcement with the modern legal
OL,14,Ftools they need to deter, detect and
OL,15,Fdisrupt the full range of state
OL,16,Fthreats.
OL,18,F"The action counter-terrorism police
OL,19,Fhave been able to take this morning is
OL,20,Fan example that that legislation is
OL,21,Fworking well."
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUzD@AOU}D@NO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
