CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1772679804
OL,3,CHusband of Labour MP questioned after
OL,4,Carrest on suspicion of spying for China
OL,6,FCommander Helen Flanagan, head of
OL,7,FCounter Terrorism Policing London,
OL,8,Fsaid: "We have seen a significant
OL,9,Fincrease in our casework relating to
OL,10,Fnational security in recent years, and
OL,11,Fwe continue to work extremely closely
OL,12,Fwith our partners to help keep the
OL,13,Fcountry safe and take action to
OL,14,Fdisrupt malign activity where we
OL,15,Fsuspect it."
OL,17,FIn addition to the addresses where the
OL,18,Fsuspects were arrested, the Met said
OL,19,Fthree other properties in London, East
OL,20,FKilbride in Scotland, and Cardiff have
OL,21,Falso been searched.
OL,26,@pD@GOUwD@LO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
