CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1772679804
OL,3,CHusband of Labour MP questioned after
OL,4,Carrest on suspicion of spying for China
OL,6,FThe force said the 39-year-old suspect
OL,7,Fwas arrested in London, the 43-year-
OL,8,Fold man was arrested in Pontyclun in
OL,9,FSouth Wales, and the 68-year-old was
OL,10,Farrested in the county of Powys in mid-
OL,11,FWales ` with all three being detained
OL,12,Funder the Police and Criminal Evidence
OL,13,FAct.
OL,15,FMs Flanagan added that the police do
OL,16,Fnot believe there to be "any imminent
OL,17,For direct threat" related to these
OL,18,Farrests.
OL,26,@xD@YOUyD@QO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
