PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1772679804
OL,3,CHusband of Labour MP questioned after
OL,4,Carrest on suspicion of spying for China
OL,6,FA Police Scotland spokesperson said:
OL,7,F"On Wednesday March 4 2026, we carried
OL,8,Fout a search of an address in East
OL,9,FKilbride on behalf of an investigation
OL,10,Fbeing led by Counter Terrorism
OL,11,FPolicing London."
OL,13,FKemi Badenoch said the Government must
OL,14,F"treat China as the threat we all know
OL,15,Fit is".
OL,17,FIn a video posted on X, the Tory
OL,18,Fleader said: "China is targeting
OL,19,FBritain, targeting our MPs. Enough.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@QO]vD@AOUwD@FO]zD@NOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30312
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1772679804
OL,3,CHusband of Labour MP questioned after
OL,4,Carrest on suspicion of spying for China
OL,6,F"Keir Starmer chose to go to Beijing
OL,7,Fand boasted about opening a direct
OL,8,Fchannel to President Xi without
OL,9,Fgetting anything in return. That was a
OL,10,Fmistake.
OL,12,F"His Government has approved China's
OL,13,Fmega-embassy in London. Worse than
OL,14,Fthat, he's making us even more reliant
OL,15,Fon Chinese goods for our energy
OL,16,Fsecurity.
OL,18,F"The Government needs to stop being
OL,19,Fnaive, grow a backbone and treat China
OL,20,Fas the threat we all know it is."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUzD@AOU|D@aO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/12
